'''乔瓦尼·费利切·桑切斯'''（{{Lang-it|'''Giovanni Felice Sances'''}}，“'''Sances'''”也写作“'''Sancies'''”“'''Sanci'''”“'''Sanes'''”或“'''Sanchez'''”，约1600年-1679年11月24日），意大利歌唱家、巴洛克时期作曲家，在世时享誉欧洲。

1609年-1614年间，桑切斯在位于[[罗马|罗马]]的{{Tsl|en|Collegio Teutonico|日耳曼大学}}学习。1614年，他曾在歌剧''Amor pudico''中上台演出。他的职业生涯始于[[博洛尼亚|博洛尼亚]]与[[威尼斯|威尼斯]]这两座城市。桑切斯的第一部歌剧''Ermiona''于1636年首次亮相，其本人也亲自登台演唱Sances studied at the [[Collegio_Germanico|Collegio Germanico]] in [[Rome|Rome]] from 1609 to 1614. He appeared in the opera ''Amor pudico'' in Rome in 1614. His career then took him to [[Bologna|Bologna]] and [[Venice|Venice]]. His first opera ''Ermiona'' was staged in [[Padua|Padua]] in 1636, in which he also sang.

1636年，桑切斯前去[[維也納|维也纳]]，在此地他最初受雇于皇家宫廷，成为一名男高音。在1649年[[斐迪南三世_(神圣罗马帝国)|斐迪南三世]]统治期间，他委任副{{Tsl|en|Kapellmeister|宫廷乐长}}，此时正乐长为{{Translink|en|Antonio Bertali|安东尼奥·贝塔利}}。二人相互协作，定期将意大利歌剧搬上舞台。桑切斯还创作了如''sepolcri''、圣乐及室内乐这些类型的作品。In 1636 he moved to [[Vienna|Vienna]], where he was initially employed at the imperial court chapel as a tenor. In 1649, during the reign of [[Ferdinand_III,_Holy_Roman_Emperor|Ferdinand III]] he was appointed vice-''Kapellmeister'' under [[Antonio_Bertali|Antonio Bertali]]. He collaborated with Bertali to stage regular performances of Italian opera. He also composed [[Sepolcro#Sepolcro|''sepolcri'']], sacred works and chamber music.

1669年贝塔利去世后，他成功任命宫廷乐长一职。出于健康原因，从1673年始，他的副手[[约翰·海因里希·施梅尔策|约翰·海因里希·施梅尔策]]逐渐承担他的工作。1679年，桑切斯逝于维也纳。In 1669 he succeeded to the post of Imperial ''[[Kapellmeister|Kapellmeister]]'' upon Bertali's death. From 1673, due to poor health, many of his duties were undertaken by his deputy [[Johann_Heinrich_Schmelzer|Jodhann Heinrich Schmelzer]]. He died in Vienna in 1679.

